        . "Nature Biotechnology 29, 644652 (2011)\n"
        . "Paper: http://www.nature.com/nbt/journal/v29/n7/full/nbt.1883.html\n"
        . "Code:  http://trinityrnaseq.sf.net\n\n\n";

=included_in_trinity
    
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
----- Tools Below are Used Within Trinity Accordingly -----------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

